parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake booster can cause the brakes to become difficult to press, leading to increased stopping distances and a higher risk of accidents.
symptoms: The brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the brake pedal is hard to press
the brakes fail to engage when the brake pedal is depressed
the vehicle stalls when braking
a hissing noise is heard when braking.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Takata airbag inflator can cause the airbag to deploy without warning, leading to injuries or accidents, or prevent the airbag from deploying in the event of a crash, increasing the risk of injury or fatality.
symptoms: Airbag deploys without warning or impact
airbag warning light illuminates
inability to repair or replace airbag due to parts unavailability.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can cause the airbag to deploy without warning, leading to injuries or accidents, or prevent the airbag from deploying in the event of a crash, increasing the risk of injury or fatality.
symptoms: Airbag deploys without warning or impact
airbag warning light illuminates
inability to repair or replace airbag due to parts unavailability.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Passenger Seat Airbag Warning Light Illumination
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The illumination of the passenger seat airbag warning light can indicate a faulty airbag system, which can lead to injuries or accidents if the airbag deploys without warning or fails to deploy in the event of a crash.
symptoms: Passenger seat airbag warning light illuminates intermittently or continuously
airbag system malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the water pump can cause the engine to shut down without warning, leading to a loss of control and potentially causing accidents.
symptoms: The water pump suddenly starts leaking
the engine shuts down without warning
the coolant floods the crankcase
and the engine is ruined.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transfer case can cause the vehicle to lose power, leading to a loss of control and potentially causing accidents. The corrosion of the transfer case can also cause a traction loss, compromising driving safety.
symptoms: The transfer case leaks
the vehicle loses power
the transmission shifts hard
the vehicle shudders when accelerating
the burned oil odor is present
and the corrosion of the transfer case is evident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake booster can cause the vehicle to lose braking power, leading to a loss of control and potentially causing accidents.
symptoms: The brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the brake booster fails
the vehicle has a hard brake
and the brake power booster needs to be replaced.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power, leading to a loss of control and potentially causing accidents.
symptoms: The transmission shifts hard
the vehicle shudders when accelerating
the transmission has a squeaking or grinding noise
and the vehicle has trouble accelerating.
